God Save The Bag, a conceptual minigame made it for fun.
The skeleton of the minigame is based on SpriteMethodTest made it for Chris Pruett.
http://code.google.com/p/apps-for-android/
This minigame only have 4 stages, I want run this game on all the android smatphones, tablets, and google tv, if it's possible. 
The link for Google-Play free-version https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.estudio.cheke.game.gstb
The link for Google-Play paid(donate)-version https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.estudio.cheke.game.gstb.premium